{"type":null,"faqId":36944,"title":"充电时注意事项？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n.p1{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span>请使用产品配套充电器充电；</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span>建议将手表固定在支架上；</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span>确保充电器插头与充电槽接触良好；</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span>电量低于25%时请及时充电；</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span>建议电池充满之后及时断开电源；</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span>尽量避免充电时使用手表；</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span>充电线妥善保存，避免插头触点损坏。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":204,"faqType":"电池&充电&功耗","useful":1,"unUseful":2,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2044","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Battery-Charging-Consumption","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1440638665000,"seriesProductName":"K1-G01","visitedTimes":91,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"荣耀小K,儿童,手表","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}